title: RL Grime - VOID
description:
Los Angeles producer RL Grime's debut album, Void, is out next week on WeDidIt. It's a star-studded collection of songs which includes collaborations with How to Dress Well (which he previously shared), Big Sean, and Djemba Djemba.

Rip of advance stream on pitchfork except for all released singles. Bitrates range from 230 to 320kbps. All up to date and correct metadata and filenames. Enjoy.
